        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.06] px-4 py-2 backdrop-blur-xl">
          Medicamentos
        </span>

        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.06] px-4 py-2 backdrop-blur-xl">
